**Monetization model worth thinking about early:**

- **Freemium** — core tracking free, AI features behind a subscription
- **Pro tier** — unlimited AI analysis, named snapshots, export features, multi-profile
- **Family plan** — what CardTracker already supports architecturally
- **API cost passthrough** — you could absorb Anthropic costs in the subscription margin rather than asking users for their own keys

The fact that AI is deeply embedded — not bolted on — is your competitive edge. Most budgeting apps treat AI as a chatbot afterthought. Yours builds strategy, applies it, tracks against it. That's a real differentiator in the App Store.

